txt.en: Infected Orcs can be found throughout Agarnaith.\n\nYou should defeat infected Orcs.
These infected Orcs are extremely dangerous. You have valiantly defeated several, but have a feeling many more lurk in the foreboding swamps of Agarnaith.
TBD Go to Agarnaith Ranger Camp
In your scouting of Agarnaith, you encounter some strange Orcs. They show signs of disease, and their behaviour is rabid and erratic.

In your scouting of Agarnaith, you encounter some strange Orcs. They show signs of disease, and their behaviour is especially erratic. You decide that you should defeat them rather than risk another dangerous encounter later. The Rangers back at the camp should be made aware of this threat.
